Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.45,0:00:12.37,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.37,0:00:15.58,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,“The Rising Voltteccers Save The Day”?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.41,0:00:19.25,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,“Another Honor to \N the Rising Voltteccers’ Name”?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.67,0:00:21.00,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,What is all this?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.54,0:00:25.51,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,The Rising Voltteccers \N have been out and about?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.51,0:00:26.26,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.59,0:00:29.63,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Seems to be making the rounds \N on some online news sites.{wadai}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.63,0:00:32.51,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,We’ve been relaxing, so who could it be...?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.51,0:00:35.89,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,That {\i1}does{\i0} look like \N the Brave Asagi... kinda...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.89,0:00:40.98,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,The Rising Voltteccers is {\i1}us!{\i0} \N I ain’t likin’ all this about fakers showin’ up!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.19,0:00:43.77,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,But it’s odd...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.77,0:00:49.78,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,{\q2}Judging by the articles, they’ve been helping \N people in trouble, and treating injured wild Pokémon...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.20,0:00:51.74,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,They’re... nice?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.74,0:00:53.66,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,They’re good guys...?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.66,0:00:56.24,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Good, bad, {\i1}whatever!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.24,0:01:00.54,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Dunno what their game is, \N but I’ll smack some sense into those fakers!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.42,0:01:04.17,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It’s not like we {\i1}know{\i0} \N that’s what they are yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.17,0:01:07.38,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,But it {\i1}is{\i0} curious. For now, \N what say we go and try to meet them?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.38,0:01:08.55,Main,Liko Dot,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:13.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:43.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.66,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Oh! If you’re looking for \N the Rising Voltteccers,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.66,0:03:03.91,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,I hear they cleaned up \N all the trash in the park!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.17,Main,Man,0,0,0,,The Rising Voltteccers...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.17,0:03:09.13,Main,Man,0,0,0,,I heard they helped \N find a lost Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.59,0:03:12.80,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,{Hmm... }They’re not here...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.80,0:03:16.05,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,They{Randoms} {\i1}did{\i0} say that \N they{Fakers} went in this direction...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.05,0:03:20.60,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,And the Brave Asagi sighting \N came from around here, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.60,0:03:24.23,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Whatever the case, \N just {\i1}how{\i0} far ahead did Ult even go...?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.23,0:03:27.73,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,He was so eager, going all \N {\i1}“I’m{\i0} gonna be the one who finds ‘em first!”
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.73,0:03:30.69,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,He’ll just have gotten himself lost, \N and eventually wind up...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.74,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,And speak of the devil...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.74,0:03:37.86,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}did{\i} get lost.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.58,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Found you, Fake Rising Voltteccers!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.08,0:03:48.04,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hold on! We’re the real ones!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.04,0:03:51.04,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Real ones? \N Gimme some proof then!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.46,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Proof?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.46,0:03:54.34,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, \N that’s a tough one.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.34,0:03:57.22,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,How do I know {\i1}you’re{\i0} not a fake Ult?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.22,0:04:01.30,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Huh?! {\i1}Obviously{\i0} I’m the bona fide,{genuine four-kanji idiom above his usual vocab} \N one-of-a-kind Almighty Ult{Honorifics note: Ult-sama}!{remove "Almighty" in honorifics track}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.60,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Then the same goes for us!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.81,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh! You’re suspicious!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.77,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.44,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.32,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,The Brave Asagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.32,0:04:14.44,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It really is our ship...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.53,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,What do we do? \N Wait and see what happens?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.95,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,What good’s that gonna do?! \N Let’s go!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.95,0:04:19.99,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.95,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,We don’t know what we’re up against.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.95,0:04:26.20,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Let’s approach cautiously.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.34,0:04:33.84,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.09,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.80,0:04:38.42,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What {\i1}is{\i0} all this?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.18,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,It’s tiny!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.18,0:04:42.22,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,A van...?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.47,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.23,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Did you need something from...?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.98,0:04:55.07,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,All of you... \N Could you really be...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.07,0:04:56.36,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,We’re back!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.32,0:05:00.24,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,We got loads!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.74,0:05:02.74,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,It’s Roy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.74,0:05:03.62,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Dearie Liko{Honorifics note: Liko-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.62,0:05:04.74,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Ms. Dot{Honorifics note: Dot-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.74,0:05:08.62,Main,Fans,0,0,0,,It’s the Rising Voltteccers! \N We’re your fans!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.62,0:05:09.66,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.66,0:05:10.62,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Fans?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.12,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Please let me shake your hand!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.63,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Please sign these!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.63,0:05:15.55,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Lemme see your Mega Ring!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.46,0:05:21.09,Main,Fans,0,0,0,,{\i1}So cute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.97,0:05:26.85,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Erm... Uh, what exactly is going on—?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.85,0:05:29.31,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Hold up! \N You ain’t got a {\i1}me{\i0} in there?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.31,0:05:31.48,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Oh no, we do!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.61,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,That’s {\i1}Yamirami,{\i0} ain’t it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.61,0:05:37.07,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,I really like you, Roy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.11,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,‘Cause you’re so super cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.49,0:05:41.36,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Cool...?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.36,0:05:46.91,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Ever since our son saw you on the news, \N he’s been a big fan of the Rising Voltteccers!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.91,0:05:51.46,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Huh?! But it was Mighty G \N that saved everyone, wasn’t it?{Intentionl scenebleed}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.46,0:05:55.29,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,All my friends like Mighty G, \N but I know the truth!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.29,0:05:58.13,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,The Rising Voltteccers \N are the {\i1}real{\i0} heroes!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.84,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,You just gotta be! Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.68,0:06:06.35,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,W-Well, I dunno, are we...? {a dismissive oh-I-wonder just like Friede's last week}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.35,0:06:11.23,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Our boy tells us he wants to go adventuring, \N just like Roy{Honorifics note: Roy-kun} and his friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.23,0:06:13.44,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,So Liko made me all this!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.44,0:06:14.81,Main,Ultfan,0,0,0,,May dis!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.81,0:06:15.48,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.23,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Tee-hee! He means me!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.23,0:06:21.94,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,And now our whole family \N is {\i1}crazy{\i0} for the Rising Voltteccers!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.57,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,All of us are passionately...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.49,Main,Fans,0,0,0,,...cheering you on!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.41,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Then, that means this...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.41,0:06:29.29,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Dot did that for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.29,0:06:29.99,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.99,0:06:35.21,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,I refurbished a van we weren’t using \N to look like the Brave Asagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.21,0:06:37.17,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Can’t fly, though!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.17,0:06:40.13,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,So our family hopped on board, \N and now we’re traveling, see!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.13,0:06:44.05,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Yeah! Feeling like \N we’re the Rising Voltteccers!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.13,0:06:48.51,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Liko! You’re so cute! \N The cutest the whole world over!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.60,0:06:54.06,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,So basically, they’re cosplayers...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.40,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I never expected \N they’d be fans of ours...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.40,0:06:58.69,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Hey! Let’s have a battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.23,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Huh? A battle?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.69,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,I wanna fight the Rising Voltteccers!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.69,0:07:05.36,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Good idea! While we have you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.36,0:07:09.41,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Could we have a battle, \N to commemorate meeting you?{Couldn't we request, to commemorate this?}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.41,0:07:10.95,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,A battle sounds great!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.95,0:07:13.96,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,I’ll give ya a bout \N with my {\i1}strongest{\i0} Yamirami!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.79,0:07:17.08,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,We’ll take you on!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.42,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.42,0:07:20.09,Main,Likofan Dotfan,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.09,0:07:22.17,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Well, if it’s for commemoration...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.72,0:07:27.59,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,All right... Let’s go, Beanie!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.43,0:07:31.06,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,And us, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.06,0:07:31.81,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.81,0:07:32.47,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Chuu-cha!{Likely from chan, maybe also chuusha=park}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.64,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Rai-o!{Male name ending, also from righty-ho/right-o}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.48,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Papa and Mama use Raichu, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.28,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,They’ve even got a Pichu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.49,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,The battle’s a 4v4!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.49,0:07:55.50,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Meaning whoever defeats \N the entire other side wins!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.25,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,And no holding back, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.79,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Yeah, for sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.75,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Beanie! Wild Volt!{The way Royfanboy enunciates boru-to~, I thought it was mimicking Volttec[cers] at first xD}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.63,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,He’s fast, \N but I can predict his trajectory!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.14,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya! \N Intercept with Magical Leaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.47,0:08:16.98,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,That’s Chuu-cha’s Cat Rattler. {ねこだまし | "Cat Tricker", to slap your hands together in front of an opponent in sumo, a move that can even surprise the quick reflexes of a cat. Probably more a sumo move than a cat move, but past usage has included cats...}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.15,0:08:21.15,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.15,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Good going!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.61,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,You’re wide open!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.57,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Yamirami! Shadow Strike!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.53,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Rai-o! 100,000 Volts!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.54,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,So bright! \N He got rid of the shadows...!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.71,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Those Raichu are strong!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.80,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Yeah, they’ve been trained well.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.80,0:08:48.38,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Beanie! Next, Wild Bolt on Wanival!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.76,0:08:52.01,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Avoid it with dance steps, Wanival!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.22,0:08:56.35,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Nice catch! Retry!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.27,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Dodge it, Loudbone!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.11,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Nice pass! Retry!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.11,0:09:06.40,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Beanie! Go, go!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.08,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I can’t predict \N where it’ll come from...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.00,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,What an incredible combo.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.75,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Let’s keep calm \N and look for our chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.25,0:09:25.25,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,If we can’t predict \N how Pikachu’s gonna be movin’...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.25,0:09:28.13,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,...then let’s take out \N the Raichu first!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.13,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Yamirami! First up’s that one!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.13,0:09:33.51,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Papa’s in danger! \N Beanie, use Thunder!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.18,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.18,0:09:43.40,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wanival! Protect everyone \N with a rotating Aqua Cutter!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.66,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,What a brilliant block!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.66,0:09:54.82,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Awesome! So cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.24,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,That’s the Rising Voltteccers for you!{Sasuga. line}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.66,0:09:59.62,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Now they’ve started praising us...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.25,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Kinda throws me off my game.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.46,0:10:05.21,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Let’s use this momentum! \N Wave Tackle!
Comment: 10,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.43,Main,Ultfan,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.31,0:10:22.23,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.40,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,What’re you playing at, Wanival?!
Comment: 10,0:10:24.40,0:10:26.36,Main,Ultfan,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.49,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It paralyzed him?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.49,0:10:42.41,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,We can’t ignore that Pichu either!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.41,0:10:44.71,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Isn’t this fun, Beanie?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.88,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,We’ll keep going! Wild Volt!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.96,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,And we’ll support you! \N Chuu-cha!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.96,0:10:52.97,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Rai-o!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.09,0:10:59.60,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I’ll make an opening! \N Then it’s up to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.85,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wanival! Head for that Raichu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.31,0:11:08.02,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,I won’t let you! \N Beanie, use Iron Tail!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.32,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.41,0:11:21.91,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,I’ll come help you now!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.91,0:11:22.66,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Chuu-cha!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.29,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Loudbone! Charm Voice!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.79,0:11:31.92,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wanival!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.88,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Change your target to Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.13,0:11:38.05,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,That Pichu again...!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.81,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Yamirami! Eerie Light!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.73,0:11:50.86,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Heh! Go take a nap.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.86,0:11:54.90,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ult! \N Wanival! Wave Tackle!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.99,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Rai-o! 100,000 Volts!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.21,0:12:08.29,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Beanie!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.63,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,That was awesome.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.05,0:12:16.13,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,You two really tried your hardest!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.55,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,You were very cool, {my }son!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.14,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.81,0:12:26.35,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Mama, it seems like the kids \N tuckered themselves out playing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.35,0:12:30.06,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Which means that, starting now, \N this is {\i1}our{\i0} time, Papa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.07,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Let’s enjoy this battle...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.61,0:12:38.32,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,...to the fullest!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.11,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mega Rings?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.49,0:12:41.70,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Chuu-cha!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.70,0:12:42.74,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Rai-o!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.49,Main,Likofan Dotfan,0,0,0,,Mega Evolve!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.51,0:13:07.47,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,The Raichu... Mega Evolved?!
Comment: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:12.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.57,0:13:21.66,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Mega Raichu...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.66,0:13:22.87,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,...X!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.28,0:13:27.16,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Mega Raichu...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.25,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,...Y!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.67,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,They’re here!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.38,0:13:35.96,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Th-They’re mega-cool, ain’t they?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.96,0:13:39.59,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Raichu Mega Evolving... \N I’ve never seen that before...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.59,0:13:41.76,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,...but you’re down to \N battle ‘em, right, Loudbone?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.14,0:13:45.51,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Let’s keep going! Masquernya!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.81,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wanival! Kick Down!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.39,0:13:52.44,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Follow it up, Yamirami! \N Use Hell Thrust!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.69,0:13:56.23,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Send Thunder crashing down!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.16,0:14:10.12,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,What’s up with the way it moves...? \N I can’t predict {\i1}that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.87,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Time to hit you hard!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.00,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Wild Volt!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.84,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Loudbone! Stomping Tantrum!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.52,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,No way... \N When did that happen...?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.77,0:14:34.39,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wanival, you fought well!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.44,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Take a break, Yamirami!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.44,0:14:42.49,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.49,0:14:44.66,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,An attack as fast as lightning!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.66,0:14:47.62,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Now, it’s 2v2! The score’s even!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.08,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Magical Leaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.20,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Flamethrower!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.83,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,EM Levitation!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.83,0:14:56.92,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Rai-o, leap on!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.67,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,They can fly?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.09,0:15:04.76,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,But Magical Leaf will still... {But Magical Leaf is...(something that won't let them avoid)}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.43,0:15:09.72,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Iron Tail!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.02,0:15:14.27,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Plus, Thunder!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.89,0:15:18.19,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,It’s hard to predict \N that Thunder’s trajectory...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.19,0:15:20.36,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Their ability to fly is an issue, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.36,0:15:21.90,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Which should we aim for first...?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.90,0:15:25.03,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Maybe... Mega Raichu Y...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.78,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Liko! Roy! I have a plan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.58,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Good going! You’re strong!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.70,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Thanks, Dot!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.96,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I bet that’ll work!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.83,0:15:38.92,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Let’s give it a try!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.92,0:15:43.05,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Loudbone! \N Aim a Flare Song right between them!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.32,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Iron Tail!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.19,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya! Lightning Speed!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.65,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Show them some Thunder!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.58,0:16:14.83,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,His tail?! What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.83,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,She tangled up his tail \N when they passed by...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.83,0:16:22.71,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,The plan worked!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.67,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,From his previous attacks,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.67,0:16:29.59,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I worked out that Mega Raichu Y uses his tail \N to amplify the electricity from his head.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.85,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Papa, I’m coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.85,0:16:33.39,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Chuu-cha!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.52,0:16:41.48,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,You leave me no choice! \N Use 100,000 Volts from your cheeks!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.11,0:16:47.36,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Counter with Magical Leaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.62,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,You did it, Masquernya!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.92,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,You won’t beat me that easily!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.92,0:17:04.25,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Chuu-cha, move!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.55,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Rargh... You sneaky little...!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.55,0:17:12.18,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya! \N Get beside Loudbone!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.51,0:17:17.14,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Oh my, you’re giving me \N a single target!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.14,0:17:18.93,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Take them down with Wild Volt!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.06,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Take the attack, Loudbone!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.90,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya, \N you hide behind Loudbone!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.66,0:17:33.28,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Dig in your heels!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.04,0:17:37.70,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,That’s not good!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.46,0:17:41.83,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Magical Leaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.34,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Flamethrower!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.85,0:18:01.31,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.31,0:18:03.81,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Thanks for trusting Loudbone \N to come through!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.81,0:18:06.61,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Sure! I had total faith \N that you’d stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.11,0:18:10.86,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,This’s the Loudbone that{ even} stopped \N Rekkuuza’s Draconic Masterstroke, after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.86,0:18:13.99,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Our combo’s the strongest there is!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.99,0:18:15.95,Main,Fans,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the best!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.95,0:18:18.95,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,You’re so strong, \N Rising Voltteccers!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.87,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Thanks for battling us!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.87,0:18:23.29,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Yeah! We got to have a great battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.50,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,We enjoyed ourselves, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.50,0:18:28.63,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Those Raichu were strong foes... \N Just who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.63,0:18:31.47,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Mama and Papa \N used to be Elite Trainers!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.47,0:18:33.72,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,In our much younger days.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.72,0:18:36.39,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,We even went and challenged \N the Pokémon League...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.39,0:18:42.93,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Your Pikachu’s got potential, too. \N Might even be like Cap someday.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.77,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.19,0:18:49.90,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,I’m so glad we got to meet \N the Rising Voltteccers!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.90,0:18:53.03,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Chances like this are so very rare!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.03,0:18:53.53,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.24,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,What brought all of you here, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.33,0:19:04.25,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,{\q2}Actually, the idea that {\i1}you{\i0} guys are the Rising Voltteccers \N seems to be making the rounds.{wadai}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.25,0:19:06.75,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,We found out \N by looking at online news.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.67,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,They thought we were the real thing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.67,0:19:13.76,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,I had no idea. \N I’m not terribly familiar with the net...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.76,0:19:17.14,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,We’ve caused you \N a whole mess of trouble then, haven’t we?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.14,0:19:18.68,Main,Likofan Dotfan,0,0,0,,We’re sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.68,0:19:20.14,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,O-Oh, no, it’s not...{...something that big}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.14,0:19:25.02,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Regardless of how much we adore you, \N we {\i1}can’t{\i0} have people making that mistake!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.02,0:19:29.15,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Do we have to stop \N playing pretend Rising Voltteccers?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.90,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Don’t stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.24,0:19:38.28,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.28,0:19:41.20,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,You’re cheering us on!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.16,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It makes us happy! {We’re happy for you to[ cosplay us]!}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.16,0:19:45.41,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Yup! You ain’t bad guys or nothin’!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.41,0:19:48.00,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,After all, it was your {\i1}good{\i0} deeds \N making the rounds!{wadai}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.50,0:19:49.71,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Everyone...!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.55,0:19:53.63,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Go and have plenty of adventures!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.01,0:19:56.51,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,We’ll be cheering you on, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.51,0:19:57.38,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.38,0:20:02.43,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,I’ll have loads of amazing adventures! \N Just like the Rising Voltteccers do!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.65,Main,Likofan,0,0,0,,Let’s set off!{出発！}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.65,0:20:15.24,Main,Dotfan,0,0,0,,Right-o!{Rai-o!}{Righty-ho!}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.99,0:20:18.32,Main,Royfan,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.16,0:20:26.20,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Kinda puts a smile on your face, \N doesn’t it? {It was happy somehow, wasn't it?}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.20,0:20:30.75,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,{\q2}Just the thought that your adventures \N ignited the spirit of adventure in someone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.67,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Yeah! So we’ve got to do \N everything we can, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.59,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,We can’t just stand around \N doing nothing!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.22,0:20:40.72,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Awright! \N Let’s get back to the ship and set off!{出発}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.57,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hey, Cap! We’re setting off!{出発}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.38,0:21:15.00,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Huh...? Cap?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.42,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Weren’t you just outside?
Comment: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:45.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie A}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.29,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Friede here!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.29,0:21:51.87,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’s time to Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.00,0:21:55.29,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Today’s topic is Raichu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.29,0:21:58.05,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Raichu is a Pokémon \N with many different forms,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.05,0:22:01.51,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,but which of these is \N a form that has yet to be found?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.01,0:22:06.47,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,See the answer after the commercials!
Comment: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:06.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:36.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie B}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.27,0:23:42.44,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Now, time to announce \N the correct answer!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.44,0:23:43.86,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,The answer is...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.86,0:23:46.49,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,C: Kyodaimax Raichu!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.99,0:23:50.24,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,If people ever {\i1}did{\i0} find one, \N you’d wanna go see it for sure, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.12,0:23:55.75,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Looks like Alolan Raichu go surfing!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.16,0:23:58.54,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,You’d wanna surf with one someday \N if you could, right?{Similar to Fred phrasing}
Comment: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.76,0:24:11.26,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Ooh, seems like you guys’re in a good mood. \N Somethin’ good happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.64,0:24:14.60,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Why’d ya clam up all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.27,0:24:21.19,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Yer eyes are mega-dartin’ \N all over the place.{me ga}{me ga oyogu, 'your eyes are swimming', going back  and forth sideways in shifty glances as if hiding something. Unclear if Ult actually gets the sus-ness or is just commentating what he sees.}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.19,0:24:22.19,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Eh, whatever!{Intentional scenebleed}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.19,0:24:24.82,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,So, to be continued \N next time on Pocket Monsters!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.82,0:24:26.74,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Secret Metamon Rhapsody
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.74,0:24:27.74,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Uh... Wh—?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.74,0:24:29.61,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Huh?! Metamon?!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
